cportage - damn fast Gentoo Linux Package Manager.
http://git.slonopotamus.org/?p=cportage

Dependencies
------------

Build time only:
 - CMake >= 2.8
 - bison (tested with 2.4.2)
 - flex(tested with 2.5.35)

Both build and runtime:
 - GLib >= 2.14

Compiling
---------
See the INSTALL document for build instructions.

Documentation
-------------
See 'doc' dir.

